title: Join GTA+
headline: Join GTA+
subtitle: Get 4X Rewards on Auto Shop Client Jobs and More
content:
Join Grand Theft Auto Online’s premium Membership program this week and you’ll receive 4X Rewards on Auto Shop Client Jobs.

You can also get 2X Rewards on Auto Shop Robbery Contract Finales, 50% off Auto Shop Properties, and Free Auto Shop Style Upgrades.

Membership renews monthly, cancel any time. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
